{"tid":2401810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"激戰！一群黑狗闖農舍  白鵝極限以一敵四  趕走入侵狗","createTime":"2021-02-10T04:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T04:23:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"262ddef6ff5fca5cc8a64d824513ee7825cd2810","tid":2401810,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T04:23:27.000Z","msg":"中國河北石家莊日前出現鵝狗大戰，有農場主人發現自己養的雞不見了，打開監視器查看，卻意外發現監視器錄下一幕激烈的鵝狗大戰。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中國媒體報導，有農場主人發現自己農場裡的雞少了幾隻，查監視器影像卻意外發現一場鵝狗大戰，有4隻黑狗鑽進柵欄內攻擊白鵝，白鵝數度遭到黑狗咬住拖行，但是仍奮力頑抗，最後成功趕跑4隻入侵者，影片曝光後引發網友討論，紛紛讚鵝是「戰神」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sPGBKSZeeII\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsPGBKSZeeII&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQrPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=27d55ca1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sPGBKSZeeII</a><br />\n<br />\n農場主人表示，鵝雖然有受傷但問題不大，而這4隻狗是隔壁鄰居所飼養，將向其追究責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3437469\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3437469&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQrPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=ac80111a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3437469&h=9642ceef\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3437469</a>"}]}